README.md
     1‚Üí# Toasty
     3‚Üí**Current status: Incubating - Toasty is not ready for production usage. The API
     4‚Üíis still evolving and documentation is lacking.**
     5‚Üí
     6‚ÜíToasty is an ORM for the Rust programming language that prioritizes ease-of-use.
     7‚ÜíIt supports both SQL databases as well as some NoSQL databases, including DynamoDB
     8‚Üíand Cassandra. Note that Toasty does not hide the database capabilities.
     9‚ÜíInstead, Toasty exposes features based on the target database.
    10‚Üí
    11‚Üí## Using Toasty
    76‚Üí## SQL and NoSQL
    91‚Üí## Application data model vs. database schema
    98‚Üí## Current status and roadmap
   117‚Üí### Contribution

